<http://www.spektrix.com/chemainustheatrefestivalsociety/event/25624AQLDNPNGHGRJLVNVLSKKLPVRSGNS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Dining - Dirty Rotten Scoundrels";
  schema:description """
	Complete your Chemainus Theatre experience with a <span class=\"BoldText\">pre‑show buffet in our Playbill Dining Room.</span> Enjoy great food, warm hospitality, and live piano entertainment - the perfect start to your theatre outing.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our chef-curated seasonal buffet includes fresh salads and starters, choice of entrées, and some decadent desserts! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Lunch, brunch, and dinner buffets</span> available on select dates.<span><br/></span>Pair your meal with a beverage from our specialty selection of <span class=\"BoldText\">wines, beers, and estate ciders.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>✨<span class=\"BoldText\">Save when you book dining with your tickets</span><span><br/></span>Discounts apply automatically at checkout.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">2026 Dining Prices</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Lunch Buffet:</span> $37</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Brunch Buffet:</span> $46</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Classic Dinner Buffet:</span> $46</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Prime Dinner Buffet:</span> $60</li></ul><span class=\"ItalicText\">+ GST. Discounts available for children and students.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://chemainustheatrefestival.ca/playbill-dining-room/\"> View Menus</a> </h2><span><br/></span>⬇️ <span class=\"BoldText\">Click BOOK TICKETS to add dining</span>
""";
